data.description: Assumable Loan at 3.5%, balance 220K. Welcome Home to your charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located in the popular Eagle's Landing. This delightful residence offers the perfect blend of comfort & convenience, making it an ideal choice for anyone seeking a cozy haven. Low maintenance yard ensures your weekends will be spent relaxing. Step inside to find an open concept kitchen, dining & living area that promotes togetherness & is perfect for entertaining. The living area has a beautiful brick wood burning fireplace & double doors that open up to a shaded patio for grilling or enjoying cool breezes. Two Primary Bedrooms with Ensuites, with one located upstairs that has an attached 3rd bedroom or Flex Room creating a perfect retreat! Located in HEB ISD, making it an excellent choice for families with school-age children. Additionally, close by shopping, parks, dining, & major transportation adds to its desirability. Too many Attributes to list here. See more details & updates in docs.
